{"id":15902,"name":"Hyperdrive Massacre","slug":"hyperdrive-massacre","url":"https:\/\/www.igdb.com\/games\/hyperdrive-massacre","created_at":1452521350728,"updated_at":1534523670708,"summary":"Hyperdrive Massacre or HDM is an 80s inspired arcade fragfest in Spacewar sauce designed around local multiplayer, focused on kinestetics, tactical and shooting skills at a very high pace.\n\nPlayers take control of a space cadillac shooting all sorts of lasers, dropping mines and raising bullet-deflecting shields, in a single-screen wrapping arena with no friction. By competing in all game modes, players are able to unlock more cars and arenas.\n\nHDM was born as a quick throwaway prototype by modifying an Asteroids template project in September 2014. By adding bullet-deflecting shields, removing the danger elements from the debris and placing another player in the scene, a frantic gameplay with plenty of possibilities for mastery emerged. The team has been working on HDM as a side project ever since, managing to land the game on the market in slightly more than a year.\n\nHDM is part of the ID@Xbox programme.","rating":40,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"total_rating":40,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[37419,32902,36977,34919,90157,25901,102178,68364,40524,16468],"tags":[1,268435488],"developers":[7011],"category":0,"game_modes":[1,2,3],"themes":[1],"genres":[32],"first_release_date":1444608000000,"platforms":[6,14,49,3],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":49,"date":1452643200000,"region":2,"human":"2016-Jan-13","y":2016,"m":1},{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1444608000000,"region":8,"human":"2015-Oct-12","y":2015,"m":10},{"category":0,"platform":14,"date":1444608000000,"region":8,"human":"2015-Oct-12","y":2015,"m":10},{"category":0,"platform":3,"date":1444608000000,"region":8,"human":"2015-Oct-12","y":2015,"m":10},{"category":0,"platform":49,"date":1452643200000,"region":8,"human":"2016-Jan-13","y":2016,"m":1}],"screenshots":[{"url":"\/\/images.igdb